Our room was comfortable with sufficient drawer and wardrobe space, free safe and adjustable heating.	There is a safe in the room as well as hair dryers in the bathroom, but no shower curtain, not a big problem for us since we didn't have to clean it.	Our room, although quite small, was fine for a short break; the bed was a little hard but everything was clean, and the wardrobe contained a safe which was free to use.	Safe and hair dryer in room.	Having worked hard over the years to secure decent accommodation at a fair price in Venice..I have finally succeeded.	The Giorgione is clean, safe, well-positioned and offers good value for money.